folder: Wallabout St. & Harrison Ave., Brooklyn, NY
text:
Wallabout Street, west side, north of Harrison Ave., to Throop Ave. In the center of the view (wagon in front thereof) is the factory
of S. Kolners and Sons, manufacturer of wagons.
October 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

View 2  Wallabout St east from, Harrison Ave. Brooklyn
P.L. Sperr photographer Sept. 25, 1941
Neg. No. A-971

folder: Wallabout St. & Harrison Ave., Brooklyn, NY
text:
Wallabout Street, adjoining the southwest corner of Harrison Avenue, looking south. Note the synagogue hemmed in between some old stables.

September 25, 1941

folder: Wallabout St. & Harrison Ave., Brooklyn, NY
